ons":["$0.56 \\mathrm{~nm}$","$0.24 \\mathrm{~nm}$","$0.96 \\mathrm{~nm}$","$0.4 \\mathrm{~nm}$"],"answer":3,"solution":"For a fcc unit cell\n$\\begin{aligned}\n& r=\\frac{\\sqrt{2} a}{4} \\\\\n& a=\\frac{4 r}{\\sqrt{2}}=2 \\sqrt{2} \\times 0.14=0.39 \\approx 0.4 \\mathrm{~nm}.\n\\end{aligned}$","type":"mcq","source":"JEE Main 2013 (09 Apr Online)","image":null}]